# time — pod i is recreated (new UID + pmm-client sidecar) ROLL_S*(i+1)
# seconds after the patch. A naive readiness poll passes instantly (old pods
# stay Ready); the spec-aware wait must block until the stagger completes.
ROLL_S = float(os.environ.get("FAKE_KUBE_ROLL_S", "0.5"))
# Device-truth simulation: the block device behind /pgdata serves this many
# IOPS (counters advance at this rate) at this utilization — the knob that
# lets tests produce capped / exceeds / inconclusive verdicts on demand.
